</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Biography 'Indian Sun' Celebrates Ravi Shankar's Centennial And Musical Legacy</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Ravi Shankar took Indian classical music to world stages and introduced the sitar to Western audiences. His influence can still be felt today, 100 years after his birth.</b>
